snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Regicide - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
++ STEAM STORE: http://store.steampowered.com/app/322910

OUT NOW - Warhammer 40,000: Regicide is now available on Steam! Regicide features powered-up pieces, variable battlefields; featured in the rich and celebrated lore of the Warhammer 40,000 universe.

Visit the website for more information: www.warhammer40kregicide.com

We welcome feedback, however any comments which contain profanity will be removed.++
